genresAdvancedInfo.name: lafayette indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Lafayette indie is a subgenre of indie rock that emerged in the city of Lafayette, Louisiana. It is characterized by its eclectic mix of musical influences, including Cajun, zydeco, and blues. Lafayette indie bands often incorporate local culture and history into their music, creating a distinct sound that is both nostalgic and forward-thinking.
